123
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,800
Not looking where you're walking because of the early morning?

124
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,800
Manager,

125
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:46,600
what are you selling?

126
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:49,200
Let me see.

127
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:53,400
These big steamed buns look good!

128
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,300
I want a few.

129
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:59,400
Are you going to do your business?

130
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:01,400
Sleeping in the early morning?

131
