134
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,500
Don't run!

135
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:13,310
- Give it back!
- Let go!

136
00:13:13,310 --> 00:13:14,900
Give it back!

137
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,800
Give it back!

138
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:25,600
Give it back!

