Master Ning, it's me.

150
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,400
Lady Lou?

151
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:30,200
Why are you here?

152
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,700
Sister Shuwan, why are you here?

153
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:41,400
Bandits are hunting down merchants in the city.

154
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:42,600
Your identities are sensitive.

155
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:44,500
I was worried that you can't go out to find food,

156
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:47,300
so, I took these from my home to give to you.

157
00:16:47,300 --> 00:16:50,000
Sister, the city is in turmoil.

158
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,700
What if you had run into danger?

159
00:16:51,700 --> 00:16:52,800
It won't.

160
00:16:52,800 --> 00:16:55,200
The place you live is only 500 meters from my home.

161
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,700
I grew up in this area.

162
00:16:56,700 --> 00:16:59,800
It would be harder to catch me in the narrow alleys than to climb to the skies.

163
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,600
Hurry! Let everyone come and eat something.

164
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:03,100
Xiao Chan.

165
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:07,700
You'll need to go into hiding for now.

166
