171
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:26,200
So, you must not go out.

172
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:29,400
What you are saying is

173
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:32,000
Lin'an has most likely fallen into enemy hands.

174
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:36,800
Lady Lou, do you know if there's any way to get out of the city?

175
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:39,400
All four city gates have been seized by the bandits.

176
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,400
There's no way of leaving the city.

177
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:42,800
Boss, I just saw them!

178
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:45,000
