187
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:09,000
Capturing the city will only take at most a day's time.

188
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:12,700
These bandits support Fang Tianlei, who is terrorizing the southwest.

189
00:19:12,700 --> 00:19:14,200
They are extremely troublesome.

190
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:16,000
To tell you the truth, we've received an order

191
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:18,200
