192
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:21,400
Defend Lin'an City to the greatest extent and evacuate the refugees.

193
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:26,200
General Yuan, you are saying evacuation is still possible?

194
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:28,000
There is a wharf not far from the north of the city,

195
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,000
