205
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:43,800
Thanks, General Yuan.

206
00:19:43,800 --> 00:19:45,200
- Thank you so much.
- Thanks, General Yuan.

207
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,700
Okay.

208
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,600
