211
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:54,700
Useless!

212
00:19:54,700 --> 00:19:56,200
A massage on the shoulders and back is the most comfortable.

213
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,400
All right.

214
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,400
Hurry and go pack your luggage!

215
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,800
Hurry!

216
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:01,000
Then, I'll go back now, too.

217
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:03,800
Sister Shuwan, leave with us.

218
00:20:03,800 --> 00:20:04,600
No, thanks.

219
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:06,600
