222
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:11,800
I will meet you at the wharf after I pick up my family.

223
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:12,800
Be careful on the way.

224
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:14,600
- We will wait for you at the wharf.
- Don't worry.

225
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:18,300
General Yuan, I will trouble you to escort Lady Lou home.

226
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:21,000
- Okay. I'll accompany you.
- Thank you.

227
00:20:26,300 --> 00:20:29,100
