Uncle.

269
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:59,300
Be quiet! Don't talk nonsense.

270
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:02,000
Are you a bad person?

271
00:23:08,200 --> 00:23:10,100
Hero, she's just a kid.

272
00:23:10,100 --> 00:23:12,000
Please, I'm begging you, don't hurt her!

273
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:14,800
Please, I'm begging you, don't hurt her!

274
00:23:14,800 --> 00:23:16,500
Please.

275
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:27,800
Kid, what did you just call me?

276
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:29,500
Uncle.

277
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:32,700
I will teach you this once.

278
00:23:32,700 --> 00:23:35,600
You can call a man like your father uncle.

279
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:38,800
But for a man as handsome as me, you should call him brother.

280
00:23:38,800 --> 00:23:39,800
Understand?

281
00:23:39,800 --> 00:23:41,200
Yes.

282
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:43,600
Good girl.

283
00:23:45,100 --> 00:23:46,100
Lock your door.

284
00:23:46,100 --> 00:23:47,200
Don't go out.

285
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,300
Store more food up.

286
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:49,500
Okay.

287
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:51,600
You must protect the safety of your Lady.

288
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:54,900
Remember. Even if I'm gone, you must protect her well.

289
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:59,100
Ning, we're ready.

290
00:24:00,100 --> 00:24:03,000
We're running for our lives, not for travel.

291
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,600
What are you doing with all those bags?

292
00:24:04,600 --> 00:24:06,100
Drop them.

293
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:09,200
There are bandits outside.

294
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:12,800
Well, do you have any proper weapons with you?

295
00:24:12,800 --> 00:24:14,300
Yes.

296
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:25,400
Feng Yuan, I can live with Shen Miao's ladle,

297
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:27,600
but what the heck are you holding?

298
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:28,600
A steamed bun.

299
00:24:28,600 --> 00:24:30,300
It can be used to hit people and fill my stomach as well.

300
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:32,000
It's quite proper.

301
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:35,000
How about I ask Geng to cook some chicken legs for you?

302
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:37,600
Enough.

303
00:24:56,549 --> 00:24:58,389
Get out.

304
00:24:58,400 --> 00:25:00,200
Come here.

305
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:01,900
Stop.

306
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:09,500
I've told you many times that

307
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:12,100
you should be fond of women.

308
00:25:12,100 --> 00:25:15,800
If you destroy such a pretty face,

309
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:18,100
it will be a waste of beauty, right?

310
00:25:23,100 --> 00:25:24,800
Take her to the back yard.

311
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:26,600
Starve her for three days.

312
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:27,700
No.

313
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:31,800
Please. Please put me down.

314
00:25:31,800 --> 00:25:33,200
Put me down.

315
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:36,700
Hunger is the best cure.

316
00:25:36,700 --> 00:25:40,400
People can agree to any requirements just for food.

317
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:42,000
Those who never suffer from hunger can never understand.

318
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:44,400
- Right?
- Yes!

319
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:46,400
Do you want to try it, too?

320
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,600
No.

321
00:25:49,600 --> 00:25:52,000
Then, keep dancing!

322
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:53,400
Come on.

323
00:26:08,800 --> 00:26:11,600
That's quite an entrance.

324
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:14,000
Here comes Commander Liu.

325
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:28,400
Commander Bao is in such a great mood

326
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:32,200
that you are even watching the opera.

327
00:26:32,200 --> 00:26:33,700
Tell me,

328
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:36,400
why are you pillaging all the girls on the streets?

329
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:40,900
Do you want to give each of your people in Xuanwei Camp a wife?

330
00:26:42,000 --> 00:26:43,300
Let me tell you,

331
00:26:43,300 --> 00:26:47,100
I opened the gate to let you in, not to loot and plunder.

332
00:26:47,100 --> 00:26:48,800
Lin'an is our base camp.

333
00:26:48,800 --> 00:26:52,000
Now that you took away their money and daughters

334
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,400
and they are boiling with resentment,

335
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:55,100
how are we supposed to keep a foothold?

336
00:26:55,100 --> 00:26:57,200
You can't blame me for this.

337
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:59,200
We agreed on it.

338
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:01,600
Your Badao Camp will take charge of public security.

339
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:05,300
Our Xuanwei Camp will collect the money and valuables.

340
00:27:05,300 --> 00:27:09,200
We are not responsible for the mess on the streets.

341
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,600
Okay.

342
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:19,000
Then I will teach anyone who creates the mess a lesson.

343
00:27:26,600 --> 00:27:28,300
Liu Xigua,

344
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:32,000
you can't run wild here

345
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:33,600
just because you're the adopted daughter of Holy Master.

346
00:27:33,600 --> 00:27:35,200
I'm telling you,

347
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:38,000
my actions were all ordered by the Holy Master.

348
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:40,100
He will arrive here tonight.

349
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:43,400
Ask him to punish me, if you can.

350
00:27:47,600 --> 00:27:49,400
Use the time wisely.

351
00:27:52,300 --> 00:27:55,500
Tan'er, the situation is urgent.

352
00:27:55,500 --> 00:27:58,900
You take the knife in case you need it.

353
00:27:58,900 --> 00:28:00,100
I don't know how to use it.

354
00:28:00,100 --> 00:28:03,200
If it falls into the enemy's hands, they may use this against me.

355
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:04,800
You keep it.

356
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:08,100
I'll take a look at the yard.

357
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:17,500
Ning, why do you have this knife?

358
00:28:19,300 --> 00:28:22,600
A friend of mine gave it to me when I left Jiangning.

359
00:28:22,600 --> 00:28:25,100
May I know if his family name is Qin?

360
00:28:25,900 --> 00:28:27,300
Yes, it is.

361
00:28:28,100 --> 00:28:31,600
We are so close, but he just gave me this little knife.

362
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:34,600
Greetings from Yuan Dingqi, Captain of the Secret Investigation Department of Lin'an City,

363
00:28:34,600 --> 00:28:36,400
Commander Ning.

364
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:40,000
General Yuan, get up please.

365
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,900
What… What does this mean?

366
00:28:41,900 --> 00:28:42,800
What department?

367
00:28:42,800 --> 00:28:46,600
This knife is from the Right Chancellor Qin Siyuan.

368
00:28:46,600 --> 00:28:49,000
It also stands for Commander in Chief of the Secret Investigation Department.

369
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:51,600
All the people in this department swore to this knife

370
00:28:51,600 --> 00:28:53,200
that they would protect Wu Dynasty's safety.

371
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:57,200
Ning, if Right Chancellor Qin really gave this to you,

372
00:28:57,200 --> 00:29:00,100
it means you're the hope of the Secret Investigation Department.

373
00:29:00,100 --> 00:29:02,500
Now, Lin'an City is on the verge of destruction.

374
00:29:02,500 --> 00:29:05,500
We are in a state of disunity.

375
00:29:05,500 --> 00:29:09,400
I beg you to stay and lead us to take back Lin'an altogether!

376
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:11,500
General Yuan, I can't. I really can't.

377
00:29:11,500 --> 00:29:13,000
I'm just a matrilocal husband.

378
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:13,800
Ning!

379
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:15,900
The Secret Investigation Department… I…

380
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,600
Oh no.

381
00:29:35,800 --> 00:29:37,800
Get out of the way.

382
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:39,300
It's Chen Damu.

383
00:29:39,300 --> 00:29:41,200
That seems to be Taiping alley.

384
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:43,300
That b*stard!

385
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:44,600
Let's go.

386
00:29:48,600 --> 00:29:50,900
Chen Damu is dead now?

387
00:29:52,800 --> 00:29:54,300
Interesting.

388
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:58,400
Goodbye, brother.

389
00:30:03,300 --> 00:30:04,800
Withdraw!

390
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:20,300
[Chen Damu]

391
00:30:20,300 --> 00:30:22,000
[Xuanwei Barracks]

392
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:25,500
What's wrong, General?

393
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:28,000
This is the Right Commander of those bandits.

394
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:29,700
The vice general of Bao Wenhan.

395
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:31,100
He just released a signal.

396
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:34,200
I guess all the bandits in the city are heading towards us.

397
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:35,700
There are many citizens in Tailing Alley.

398
00:30:35,700 --> 00:30:38,200
If there's a fight, casualties will be inevitable.

399
00:30:39,500 --> 00:30:42,600
Tell all the citizens nearby to go to the wharf right away.

400
00:30:42,600 --> 00:30:44,000
Yes.

401
00:30:44,800 --> 00:30:47,400
General, if you are going to withstand the bandits in the whole city

402
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:50,200
with so few of you, isn't it suicide?

403
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:52,000
The longer we can hold them back for,

404
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,700
the more of our citizens will survive.

405
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:55,300
Don't worry about us, Ning.

406
00:30:55,300 --> 00:30:57,600
I'll have your family and you escorted.

407
00:30:57,600 --> 00:30:59,300
Time to leave.

408
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,400
General,

409
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:06,600
did you just kill them with gunpowder?

410
00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:08,300
- Yes.
- Do you have more?

411
00:31:08,300 --> 00:31:10,200
The main weapons have been taken.

412
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:12,700
I only have some left on the carriage.

413
00:31:12,700 --> 00:31:14,300
Wait for me.

414
00:31:15,400 --> 00:31:16,800
What's wrong?

415
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,900
You go to the wharf first.

416
00:31:21,600 --> 00:31:23,500
I'll meet you in a minute.

417
00:31:24,600 --> 00:31:27,400
Are you going to stay to stop the bandits?

418
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:32,700
If you stay, I won't leave, either.

419
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,400
If we fail to keep this place,

420
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:36,200
every one of you won't be able to escape.

421
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:37,200
You go there first.

422
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:38,400
I will catch up.

423
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,800
No, it's too dangerous.

424
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:41,700
- Geng.
- Yes.

425
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:43,200
- Take your Lady away.
- Yes.

426
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,200
How dare you!

427
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:45,400
My Lady, let's go!

428
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:46,200
Ning Liheng!

429
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,900
My Lady, let's go!

430
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:56,000
Attention, Wude Camp!

431
00:31:57,800 --> 00:32:00,600
Gather all of our people here.

432
00:32:00,600 --> 00:32:03,600
Let's fight the bandits!

433
00:32:03,600 --> 00:32:05,200
Yes.

434
00:32:15,100 --> 00:32:18,000
I'm warning you b*stards with your empty words.

435
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:21,600
Now we should carry out the north expedition while Jing is still weak.

436
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:23,500
If not now, when?

437
00:32:24,200 --> 00:32:25,600
You have no idea about state affairs.

438
00:32:25,600 --> 00:32:26,600
Stop all this nonsense.

439
00:32:26,600 --> 00:32:28,600
Jing just destroyed Liang. Its army is powerful right now!

440
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:30,300
If we go against them rashly,

441
00:32:30,300 --> 00:32:32,600
we will burn ourselves and have our people in danger!

442
00:32:32,600 --> 00:32:35,000
Now that the bandits in Lin'an haven't been wiped out,

443
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,300
yet they are pillaging and looting, waiting to expand their strength.

444
00:32:37,300 --> 00:32:39,200
If we are between a hammer and anvil,

445
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:41,200
Wu will be put in great danger!

446
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:43,000
You're talking nonsense!

447
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:44,800
The Secret Investigation Department has received a message that

448
00:32:44,800 --> 00:32:46,800
Jing has lost half of their elite force.

449
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:48,600
They can't be powerful right now.

450
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:51,700
You must have taken their bribes.

451
00:33:03,100 --> 00:33:04,800
Your Majesty,

452
00:33:04,800 --> 00:33:07,100
the courtiers have been waiting for a long time.

453
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:09,800
I wonder when you will be available for discussion.

454
00:33:09,800 --> 00:33:11,400
No hurry.

455
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:14,200
Allow me to think about it.

456
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:20,800
I wonder if you are hesitated about the…

457
00:33:22,600 --> 00:33:27,300
I have issued a decree to attack Jing.

458
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:30,800
Now, the whole world knows.

459
00:33:30,800 --> 00:33:32,800
If I suddenly go back on my word,

460
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:37,200
the world will mock me.

461
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:41,500
But now

462
00:33:42,300 --> 00:33:46,800
Lin'an is being occupied by some bandits.

463
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:50,100
Lin'an is our Wu Dynasty's military stronghold

464
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:53,200
and also a granary for the country.

465
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:56,600
If there is a mishap that occurs,

466
00:33:56,600 --> 00:33:59,800
let alone the north invasion on Jing,

467
00:33:59,800 --> 00:34:03,600
there would be effects on having a full meal.

468
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:06,200
The war in Lin'an is not over.

469
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:10,800
I dare not rashly send out troops to the northern invasion.

470
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,700
I ask Your Majesty to rest assured.

471
00:34:13,600 --> 00:34:16,700
Lin'an is full of elite soldiers from the Secret Investigation Department.

472
00:34:16,700 --> 00:34:19,600
At the same time, Wude Camp is supresssing the bandits.

473
00:34:19,600 --> 00:34:22,000
Within the next few days, the situation can be stabilized.

474
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:25,100
It will in no way affect our plan to invade the north.

475
00:34:25,100 --> 00:34:30,000
In addition, I have a surefire plan.

476
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:36,000
What is it?

477
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:38,800
Jing has just merged with Liang.

478
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:40,800
Its strength is greatly damaged at this time.

479
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:46,200
I suggest Dong Daofu lead the main army to go north.

480
00:34:46,200 --> 00:34:49,200
At the same time, two small generals will be sent to lead the forbidden army to the south

481
00:34:49,200 --> 00:34:53,000
to cooperate with our troops in Lin'an City.

482
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:55,600
In less than a month, we can get rid of the bandits.

483
00:34:55,600 --> 00:34:58,000
Then all the gunpowder and firearms will be taken up north

484
00:34:58,000 --> 00:35:00,500
to join General Dong.

485
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:03,600
Jing will definitely be defeated.

486
00:35:05,300 --> 00:35:07,600
You're very thoughtful.

487
00:35:07,600 --> 00:35:10,300
You are deserving of the trust the late Emperor placed on you.

488
00:35:11,600 --> 00:35:15,300
It's just that court is dismissed today.

489
00:35:16,200 --> 00:35:18,800
No state affairs shall be discussed.

490
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,000
Your Majesty!

491
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:22,000
You may leave now.

492
00:35:44,200 --> 00:35:46,000
Minister.

493
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:54,200
- Minister, today the Emperor...
- I know.

494
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:58,400
Today there was no court for discussion.

495
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:04,400
Of course, everything that happens in court doesn't escape your discerning eyes.

496
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:06,100
Hearing about the attack in Lin'an,

497
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:09,200
the Minister of Personnel and Minister of Defense came out all a sudden

498
00:36:09,200 --> 00:36:11,700
and opposed the north expedition.

499
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:14,800
Tong Ke and Li Gang even

500
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:18,200
had a fight outside the Imperial Study.

501
00:36:18,200 --> 00:36:19,800
It was quite a sight!

502
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:27,600
You just want to watch them fight!

503
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:31,000
But do you know Qin Siyuan talked to His Majesty

504
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:33,600
privately for two hours in the Imperial Study?

505
00:36:34,830 --> 00:36:37,789
He did go to meet the Emperor.

506
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:42,000
But I heard from Eunuch Li that he had a gloomy complexion and knitted brows

507
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,600
when he came out.

508
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:46,900
The Emperor didn't issue any decree, either.

509
00:36:46,900 --> 00:36:50,800
That means the Emperor hasn't made up his mind as well.

510
00:36:50,800 --> 00:36:53,800
I ask Minister to not be worried.

511
00:37:01,500 --> 00:37:05,000
One needs to prepare beforehand

512
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:07,900
and not be making last-minute efforts after it occurs.

513
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:11,400
If I were as careless as you,

514
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:16,000
I reckon I would have already lost my position and had my property confiscated by Qin Siyuan.

515
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:19,600
Minister is correct in teaching me.

516
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:24,800
Send someone to buy a sweet red bean cake

517
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:27,500
at Huaxiang Restaurant in the east of the city.

518
00:37:28,600 --> 00:37:31,000
Use the biggest tapestry box to package it.

519
00:37:35,200 --> 00:37:36,800
It's hot today.

520
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:39,000
Add some ice to it.

521
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:40,800
Don't let it melt.

522
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:43,200
Yes, Minister.

523
00:37:43,200 --> 00:37:44,600
Go ahead.

524
00:38:02,600 --> 00:38:04,200
Are there only these few boxes?

525
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:06,800
There is a large number of bandits, so these are being depleted quickly.

526
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:08,200
These four boxes are all we have.

527
00:38:08,200 --> 00:38:10,900
Just with these four boxes is far from enough.

528
00:38:12,100 --> 00:38:13,600
Unless…

529
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:29,000
Catch them!

530
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:47,600
Brother Li, stop trembling or else they will find us!

531
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:49,400
I'm not trembling. Shen Miao is!

532
00:38:49,400 --> 00:38:51,400
I'm not! It's your heart that is trembling.

533
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:53,100
You're trembling too much!

534
00:38:53,100 --> 00:38:55,100
I… I…

535
00:39:02,600 --> 00:39:05,400
Everyone, come! It's safe now. Let's go.

536
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:07,500
My Lady, let's go.

